snippet.title: Firewatch - September 2016 Trailer
snippet.description:
Firewatch is now available on Steam, Xbox One, and PlayStation 4
Now with a new free roam mode and behind the scenes commentary scavenger hunt!
http://firewatchgame.com

Firewatch is a mystery set in the Wyoming wilderness, where your only emotional lifeline is the person on the other end of a handheld radio.
